for
1 AN ACT relating to defense forces and affairs; expanding
2 eligibility for the Wyoming national guard member referral
3 incentive program; providing a definition; and providing
4 for an effective date.
5
6 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
7
8 Section 1. W.S. 19-9-403(e)(intro), (i), (ii), (iv)
9 by creating a new subparagraph (C) and by renumbering (C)
10 as (D) is amended to read:
11
12 19-9-403. Pay and allowances of officers and enlisted
13 persons in active state service and state active duty;
